{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Setu Solutions Engineer Assignment","version":"0.1.0"},"paths":{"/events":{"post":{"tags":["events"],"summary":"Ingest a payment lifecycle event","description":"Ingest a single payment lifecycle event.\n\nReturns 201 when the event is accepted (first time seeing this event_id).\nReturns 200 when the event is a duplicate — the request is well-formed,\nbut nothing changed on the server.","operationId":"ingest_event_events_post","requestBody":{"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/EventIngestRequest"}}},"required":true},"responses":{"201":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/EventIngestResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/transactions":{"get":{"tags":["transactions"],"summary":"List transactions with filters, sorting and pagination","description":"List transactions. All filters are optional and AND-composed.","operationId":"list_transactions_transactions_get","parameters":[{"name":"merchant_id","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Exact-match merchant ID","title":"Merchant Id"},"description":"Exact-match merchant ID"},{"name":"status","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Exact-match current status","title":"Status"},"description":"Exact-match current status"},{"name":"date_from","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Lower bound on initiated_at (inclusive)","title":"Date From"},"description":"Lower bound on initiated_at (inclusive)"},{"name":"date_to","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Upper bound on initiated_at (inclusive)","title":"Date To"},"description":"Upper bound on initiated_at (inclusive)"},{"name":"sort","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"string","description":"Sort field with optional '-' prefix for descending. Allowed: initiated_at, amount, current_status, updated_at.","default":"-initiated_at","title":"Sort"},"description":"Sort field with optional '-' prefix for descending. Allowed: initiated_at, amount, current_status, updated_at."},{"name":"limit","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","maximum":200,"minimum":1,"description":"Page size (max 200)","default":50,"title":"Limit"},"description":"Page size (max 200)"},{"name":"offset","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","minimum":0,"description":"Offset-based pagination cursor","default":0,"title":"Offset"},"description":"Offset-based pagination cursor"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionListResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/transactions/{transaction_id}":{"get":{"tags":["transactions"],"summary":"Get a single transaction's current state plus its full event history","description":"Return the materialized transaction + every event we've received for it.\n\nFastAPI validates `transaction_id` as a UUID automatically — a malformed\nvalue returns 422 before this handler runs. If the UUID is well-formed but\nrefers to a transaction we've never ingested, we return 404.","operationId":"get_transaction_transactions__transaction_id__get","parameters":[{"name":"transaction_id","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Transaction Id"}}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionDetailResponse"}}}},"404":{"description":"Transaction not found"},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/reconciliation/summary":{"get":{"tags":["reconciliation"],"summary":"Aggregate transaction counts + totals grouped by merchant × date × status","description":"Return filter-wide totals plus a per-(merchant, date, status) breakdown.\n\nDates are bucketed on UTC-day boundaries. No pagination: the grouped\nresult is bounded by merchants × days × 4 statuses, which stays small\neven over a full year.","operationId":"get_summary_reconciliation_summary_get","parameters":[{"name":"merchant_id","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Exact-match merchant ID","title":"Merchant Id"},"description":"Exact-match merchant ID"},{"name":"status","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Exact-match current status","title":"Status"},"description":"Exact-match current status"},{"name":"date_from","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Lower bound on initiated_at (inclusive)","title":"Date From"},"description":"Lower bound on initiated_at (inclusive)"},{"name":"date_to","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Upper bound on initiated_at (inclusive)","title":"Date To"},"description":"Upper bound on initiated_at (inclusive)"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ReconciliationSummaryResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/reconciliation/discrepancies":{"get":{"tags":["reconciliation"],"summary":"Transactions in inconsistent or stuck states","description":"Return transactions flagged by one or more discrepancy detectors.\n\nDetectors:\n  - conflicting_events — same txn has both payment_failed AND settled events.\n  - stuck_in_processed — current_status=processed, processed_at past threshold.\n  - stuck_in_initiated — current_status=initiated, initiated_at past threshold.\n\nA transaction flagged by multiple detectors appears once per detector type,\nso the client can show full context without deduping.","operationId":"get_discrepancies_reconciliation_discrepancies_get","parameters":[{"name":"merchant_id","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Exact-match merchant ID","title":"Merchant Id"},"description":"Exact-match merchant ID"},{"name":"type","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancyType"},{"type":"null"}],"description":"Filter to one discrepancy type. If omitted, all detectors run.","title":"Type"},"description":"Filter to one discrepancy type. If omitted, all detectors run."},{"name":"processed_stale_hours","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","minimum":1,"description":"Flag processed txns whose processed_at is older than this many hours","default":24,"title":"Processed Stale Hours"},"description":"Flag processed txns whose processed_at is older than this many hours"},{"name":"initiated_stale_hours","in":"query","required":false,"schema":{"type":"integer","minimum":1,"description":"Flag initiated txns whose initiated_at is older than this many hours","default":1,"title":"Initiated Stale Hours"},"description":"Flag initiated txns whose initiated_at is older than this many hours"}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ReconciliationDiscrepanciesResponse"}}}},"422":{"description":"Validation Error","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"}}}}}}},"/":{"get":{"summary":"Read Root","operationId":"read_root__get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"additionalProperties":{"type":"string"},"type":"object","title":"Response Read Root  Get"}}}}}}},"/health":{"get":{"summary":"Health","description":"End-to-end check: if this returns ok, the app can reach the database.","operationId":"health_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"additionalProperties":{"type":"string"},"type":"object","title":"Response Health Health Get"}}}}}}}},"components":{"schemas":{"DiscrepancyFilters":{"properties":{"merchant_id":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Merchant Id"},"type":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancyType"},{"type":"null"}]},"processed_stale_hours":{"type":"integer","title":"Processed Stale Hours","default":24},"initiated_stale_hours":{"type":"integer","title":"Initiated Stale Hours","default":1}},"type":"object","title":"DiscrepancyFilters"},"DiscrepancyItem":{"properties":{"type":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancyType"},"transaction_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Transaction Id"},"merchant_id":{"type":"string","title":"Merchant Id"},"merchant_name":{"type":"string","title":"Merchant Name"},"amount":{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*\\d*\\.?\\d*$","title":"Amount"},"currency":{"type":"string","title":"Currency"},"current_status":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},"initiated_at":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Initiated At"},"processed_at":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Processed At"},"failed_at":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Failed At"},"settled_at":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Settled At"},"detail":{"type":"string","title":"Detail"}},"type":"object","required":["type","transaction_id","merchant_id","merchant_name","amount","currency","current_status","detail"],"title":"DiscrepancyItem","description":"One flagged transaction. Shape mirrors TransactionListItem so clients\ncan reuse the same rendering component, with a discriminator on `type`."},"DiscrepancySummary":{"properties":{"total":{"type":"integer","title":"Total"},"by_type":{"additionalProperties":{"type":"integer"},"propertyNames":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancyType"},"type":"object","title":"By Type"}},"type":"object","required":["total","by_type"],"title":"DiscrepancySummary"},"DiscrepancyType":{"type":"string","enum":["conflicting_events","stuck_in_processed","stuck_in_initiated"],"title":"DiscrepancyType","description":"Types of discrepancies the detector flags.\n\nKept as a string enum (rather than free-form) so clients can switch on it\nwithout fuzzy matching, and so OpenAPI docs enumerate the values."},"EventHistoryItem":{"properties":{"event_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Event Id"},"event_type":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/EventType"},"amount":{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*\\d*\\.?\\d*$","title":"Amount"},"currency":{"type":"string","title":"Currency"},"event_timestamp":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","title":"Event Timestamp"},"received_at":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","title":"Received At"}},"type":"object","required":["event_id","event_type","amount","currency","event_timestamp","received_at"],"title":"EventHistoryItem","description":"One event in a transaction's history timeline.\n\nDeliberately excludes raw_payload — that's audit data, not product data. If a\nfuture caller needs it, expose via `?include=raw_payload` rather than making\nevery response heavier by default."},"EventIngestRequest":{"properties":{"event_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Event Id"},"event_type":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/EventType"},"transaction_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Transaction Id"},"merchant_id":{"type":"string","maxLength":50,"title":"Merchant Id"},"merchant_name":{"type":"string","maxLength":255,"title":"Merchant Name"},"amount":{"anyOf":[{"type":"number","exclusiveMinimum":0.0},{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*(?:\\d{0,12}|(?=[\\d.]{1,15}0*$)\\d{0,12}\\.\\d{0,2}0*$)"}],"title":"Amount"},"currency":{"type":"string","maxLength":3,"minLength":3,"title":"Currency","default":"INR"},"timestamp":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","title":"Timestamp"}},"type":"object","required":["event_id","event_type","transaction_id","merchant_id","merchant_name","amount","timestamp"],"title":"EventIngestRequest","description":"Matches the shape of each object in sample_events.json."},"EventIngestResponse":{"properties":{"status":{"type":"string","title":"Status"},"event_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Event Id"},"transaction_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Transaction Id"},"current_status":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},{"type":"null"}]}},"type":"object","required":["status","event_id","transaction_id"],"title":"EventIngestResponse","description":"Returned from POST /events.\n\nstatus is 'accepted' for a new event, 'duplicate' if we'd already ingested\nthis event_id. current_status is null in the duplicate case because we don't\nre-read the transaction row on a short-circuit."},"EventType":{"type":"string","enum":["payment_initiated","payment_processed","payment_failed","settled"],"title":"EventType"},"HTTPValidationError":{"properties":{"detail":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ValidationError"},"type":"array","title":"Detail"}},"type":"object","title":"HTTPValidationError"},"Pagination":{"properties":{"total":{"type":"integer","title":"Total"},"limit":{"type":"integer","title":"Limit"},"offset":{"type":"integer","title":"Offset"}},"type":"object","required":["total","limit","offset"],"title":"Pagination"},"ReconciliationDiscrepanciesResponse":{"properties":{"filters":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancyFilters"},"summary":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancySummary"},"discrepancies":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/DiscrepancyItem"},"type":"array","title":"Discrepancies"}},"type":"object","required":["filters","summary","discrepancies"],"title":"ReconciliationDiscrepanciesResponse"},"ReconciliationSummaryResponse":{"properties":{"filters":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SummaryFilters"},"totals":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SummaryTotals"},"groups":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/SummaryGroup"},"type":"array","title":"Groups"}},"type":"object","required":["filters","totals","groups"],"title":"ReconciliationSummaryResponse"},"StatusBreakdown":{"properties":{"count":{"type":"integer","title":"Count"},"total_amount":{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*\\d*\\.?\\d*$","title":"Total Amount"}},"type":"object","required":["count","total_amount"],"title":"StatusBreakdown","description":"Per-status aggregate inside the filter-wide totals."},"SummaryFilters":{"properties":{"merchant_id":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Merchant Id"},"status":{"anyOf":[{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},{"type":"null"}]},"date_from":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Date From"},"date_to":{"anyOf":[{"type":"string","format":"date-time"},{"type":"null"}],"title":"Date To"}},"type":"object","title":"SummaryFilters","description":"Echo of the filters the caller passed — lets the client confirm scope."},"SummaryGroup":{"properties":{"merchant_id":{"type":"string","title":"Merchant Id"},"merchant_name":{"type":"string","title":"Merchant Name"},"date":{"type":"string","format":"date","title":"Date"},"status":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},"count":{"type":"integer","title":"Count"},"total_amount":{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*\\d*\\.?\\d*$","title":"Total Amount"}},"type":"object","required":["merchant_id","merchant_name","date","status","count","total_amount"],"title":"SummaryGroup","description":"One row in the grouped breakdown: (merchant × date × status)."},"SummaryTotals":{"properties":{"transaction_count":{"type":"integer","title":"Transaction Count"},"total_amount":{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*\\d*\\.?\\d*$","title":"Total Amount"},"by_status":{"additionalProperties":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/StatusBreakdown"},"propertyNames":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionStatus"},"type":"object","title":"By Status"}},"type":"object","required":["transaction_count","total_amount","by_status"],"title":"SummaryTotals","description":"Top-line snapshot over the entire filtered set.\n\nKept flat + simple so it renders as a header card without the client doing\nany folding. The per-status dict is keyed by TransactionStatus — that gives\nfour predictable keys in the JSON: initiated / processed / failed / settled."},"TransactionDetailResponse":{"properties":{"transaction":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/TransactionListItem"},"events":{"items":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/EventHistoryItem"},"type":"array","title":"Events"}},"type":"object","required":["transaction","events"],"title":"TransactionDetailResponse","description":"Full picture of one transaction: materialized state + append-only log.\n\nThe `transaction` block is the derived current state (same shape as the list\nitem, so clients can reuse rendering code). The `events` array is every\nevent we've received for this transaction, ordered oldest-first — proof of\n*why* the state is what it is, including out-of-order or duplicate arrivals."},"TransactionListItem":{"properties":{"transaction_id":{"type":"string","format":"uuid","title":"Transaction Id"},"merchant_id":{"type":"string","title":"Merchant Id"},"merchant_name":{"type":"string","title":"Merchant Name"},"amount":{"type":"string","pattern":"^(?!^[-+.]*$)[+-]?0*\\d*\\.?\\d*$","title":"Amount"},"currenc